=声音异常(15条目)=


==[[HP:0001608]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0001608
| 名称 = Abnormality of the voice
| 定义 = Any abnormality of the voice.
| 中文译名 = 声音异常
| 中文定义 = 嗓音的任何异常。
}}


==[[HP:0001609]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0001609
| 名称 = Hoarse voice
| 定义 = Hoarseness refers to a change in the pitch or quality of the voice, with the voice sounding weak, very breathy, scratchy, or husky.
| 中文译名 = 声音嘶哑
| 中文定义 = 声音嘶哑是指声音的音调或质量的变化，声音听起来虚弱，带着很重的呼吸声，有摩擦音或沙哑。
}}


==[[HP:0001611]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0001611
| 名称 = Nasal speech
| 定义 = A type of speech characterized by the presence of an abnormally increased nasal airflow during speech, associated with incomplete or weak closure of the velum.
| 中文译名 = 鼻音很重
| 中文定义 = 一种构音特点，讲话时因鼻腔气流异常增加所致，与软腭关闭不全或削弱有关。
}}


