==[[HP:0001618]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0001618
| 名称 = Dysphonia
| 定义 = An impairment in the ability to produce voice sounds.
| 中文译名 = 发音困难
| 中文定义 = 产生声音的能力减弱。
}}


==[[HP:0001620]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0001620
| 名称 = High pitched voice
| 定义 = An abnormal increase in the pitch (frequency) of the voice.
| 中文译名 = 高音调的声音
| 中文定义 = 嗓音音调（频率）的异常升高。
}}


==[[HP:0001621]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0001621
| 名称 = Weak voice
| 定义 = Reduced intensity (volume) of speech.
| 中文译名 = 嗓音微弱
| 中文定义 = 语音的强度（音量）减弱。
}}


